<section class="d-slider-blocks" data-aos="fade-in"  data-aos-delay="200">
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-1"></div>
            <div class="col-lg-11">
                <div class="carousel-slider-blocks">
                                            <div class="carousel-cell">
                                                            <p class="t-italic">He gave in and the Ritz Barcelona was built</p>
                                <p>Francesc Camb&oacute;, a politician and intellectual, insisted that Barcelona needed to have a first-class hotel, like the Ritz in Madrid. This was especially important with events like the 1929 Barcelona International Exposition pending.</p>
                                                        <picture>
                                                                    <source data-srcset="https://www.hotelpalacebarcelona.com/assets/themes/www.hotelpalacebarcelona.com/img/rooms_blocks/Planos-de-la-fachada-El-Palace.tmedium.webp" type="image/webp" srcset="">
                                                                <img data-src="https://www.hotelpalacebarcelona.com/assets/themes/www.hotelpalacebarcelona.com/img/rooms_blocks/Planos-de-la-fachada-El-Palace.tmedium.jpg"
                                     class="lazy img-fluid w-100"
                                     alt="He gave in and the Ritz Barcelona was built"
                                     title="He gave in and the Ritz Barcelona was built" src="">
                            </picture>
                                                    </div>
                                            <div class="carousel-cell">
                                                        <picture>
                                                                    <source data-srcset="https://www.hotelpalacebarcelona.com/assets/themes/www.hotelpalacebarcelona.com/img/rooms_blocks/Logo-1919-Ritz-Hotel-El-Palace-Barcelona.tmedium.webp" type="image/webp" srcset="">
                                                                <img data-src="https://www.hotelpalacebarcelona.com/assets/themes/www.hotelpalacebarcelona.com/img/rooms_blocks/Logo-1919-Ritz-Hotel-El-Palace-Barcelona.tmedium.jpg"
                                     class="lazy img-fluid w-100"
                                     alt="The architect of the modern hotel industry"
                                     title="The architect of the modern hotel industry" src="">
                            </picture>
                                                            <p class="t-italic">The architect of the modern hotel industry</p>
                                <p>At first, C&eacute;sar Ritz did not want to build one of his famous hotels in Barcelona. He planned to reserve these architectural gems for the important capital cities of the world like London, Paris, and Madrid.</p>
                                                    </div>
